@anselor cmd2 will still be supporting Python 2.7 until the end of August 2018.  Optional type hinting is only available in Python 3.  So you will need to remove your usage of optional type hinting.

Also, there appear to be a lot of unit test failures for every version of Python other than 3.5.

We currently support versions 2.7, 3.4, 3.5, 3.6, and 3.7.

